---
title: Cheesy Beef Rissoles & Kumara Fries with Caramelised Onion & Mayo Dressing
description: Rissoles are a crowd-pleasing dinnertime winner, but when you cover them with cheese and sweet caramelised onion, they’re even harder to refuse! This colourful plate also gets a serve of kumara fries and a family-friendly salad for a rainbow of delights.
